Package: plda
Type: Package
Title: Parallelizable Markov chain Monte Carlo Algorithms 
    for the Latent Dirichlet Allocation Model
Version: 0.2
Date: 2020-07-05
Author: Clint P. George and Hani Doss
Maintainer: Clint P. George <clint@iitgoa.ac.in>
URL: https://github.com/clintpgeorge/plda
Description: This package implements Grouped Gibbs, Partially Collapsed 
    Gibbs, and Collapsed Gibbs sampling algorithms for the latent Dirichlet 
    allocation (LDA) model.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.2),
    Rcpp (>= 0.12.2),
    RcppArmadillo (>= 0.7.700.0.0),
    lattice (>= 0.20-35)
LinkingTo: 
    Rcpp, 
    RcppArmadillo
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
SystemRequirements: C++11
Encoding:UTF-8
